{"tid":1891261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭根本係好典型嘅反社會人格，難怪佢可以做得咁差","createTime":"2020-02-21T16:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T21:59:59.000Z","uid":58998,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce943c6391c1a9ced8bf7051adacf73e1aef9ec","tid":1891261,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T16:58:07.000Z","msg":"反社會人格患者在初識時，往往予人理性、高EQ、善良、隨和、低調、謙遜、無害的印象，甚至顯得更有魅力，但他們缺乏同理心、悔恨和羞恥的心理特質，使得他們為人處世自私自利又衝動，同時他們善於偽裝欺騙，也善於操縱人際關係。<br />\n<br />\n完全係林鄭嘅寫照，依類人根本無同情心，所以佢根本唔會明香港人嘅痛苦<br />\n由警暴、開槍、死人、去到買唔到口罩，佢根本完全無感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己就唔撚洗理港人會點"},{"pid":"167162bed9fe101bc682daa55bede82617fc732d","tid":1891261,"uid":21757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢根本冇係領袖才能，只能做助手<br />\n決策一塌糊塗"},{"pid":"c50408bae215ccd50b784f80c0fde1f6bdda3c4b","tid":1891261,"uid":58998,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"167162bed9fe101bc682daa55bede82617fc732d","tid":1891261,"uid":21757,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"佢根本冇係領袖才能，只能做助手<br />\n決策一塌糊塗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:27:26.000Z","msg":"廢撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上位靠刷鞋"},{"pid":"ee2227d6c7d8018b783032de46940641fcb578f8","tid":1891261,"uid":242605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位手足幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極速訂閱 黃色頻道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysDa7aZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysDa7aZ.gif&h=d8854f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCdgu47O1Wlw&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=b30d6647\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Cdgu47O1Wlw</a><br />\n［黃藍YOUTUBE大戰正式開打］兩大快速